article.description: — Tyler Nelson scored 18 points as Navy beat Mount St. Mary's 75-59 on Saturday.
article.headline: Navy takes down Mount St. Mary's 75-59
article.linkText: Navy takes down Mount St. Mary's 75-59
article.story: ANNAPOLIS, Md. -- — Tyler Nelson scored 18 points as Navy beat Mount St. Mary's 75-59 on Saturday. Nelson shot 7 for 8, including 4 for 4 from beyond the arc for the Midshipmen (5-1). Daniel Deaver scored 14 points while finishing 7 of 11 from the floor, and added six rebounds, six assists, and three steals. Kam Summers recorded 14 points and shot 6 for 8, including 2 for 4 from beyond the arc. Jalen Benjamin finished with 12 points for the Mountaineers (3-4). Dakota Leffew added 10 points for Mount St. Mary's. George Tinsley also put up nine points, six rebounds and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
